<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=1200">
    <link href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="/js/handlebars.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-custom1 container-fluid p-0"> 
    
    <nav class="navbar border-bottom border-dark border-2 py-3 px-5">
        <a class="navbar-brand brand-font fs-3 text-uppercase fw-bold text-dark text-decoration-none" href="#">
            { NULL<span class="text-accent">PTR</span> }
        </a>
        <div class="d-flex gap-4 align-items-center">
            <a href="#" class="nav-link fw-bold text-uppercase text-dark p-0">Все вакансии</a>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-dark rounded-0 border-dark border-2 fw-bold text-uppercase">Для компаний</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero-section border-bottom border-dark border-2">
        <div class="row g-0">
            <div class="col-8 hero-content py-5 px-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center border-end border-dark border-2">
                <h1 class="hero-title display-1 brand-font text-uppercase lh-1 mb-4 fw-bold" style="font-size: 5rem;">
                    Пиши код.<br>
                    Не пиши<br>
                    <span class="text-accent">отписки.</span>
                </h1>
                
                <p class="hero-description fs-4 mb-5 w-75">
                    Платформа для инженеров. Курированные вакансии без скрытых условий и тестовых заданий на все выходные.
                </p>

                <div>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-danger btn-lg rounded-0 border-dark border-2 px-5 py-3 fw-bold text-uppercase">
                        Смотреть вакансии
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div> 
            <div class="col-4 hero-visual d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center bg-dark text-white p-5" style="min-height: 60vh;">
                <div class="brand-font text-accent fw-bold mb-4" style="font-size: 10rem; line-height: 1;">*</div>
                <code class="text-white fs-5 font-monospace">while(alive) { code(); }</code>
            </div> 
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features-section border-bottom border-dark border-2">
        <div class="row g-0">
            <div class="col-4 magazine-col bg-white">
                <h2 class="display-5 brand-font mb-4 fw-bold">01</h2>
                <h3 class="h4 brand-font mb-3 fw-bold text-uppercase">Прямые контакты</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">Никаких HR-фильтров с вопросами "кем вы видите себя через 5 лет". Сразу общайтесь с техлидами и CTO.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 magazine-col bg-white">
                <h2 class="display-5 brand-font mb-4 fw-bold">02</h2>
                <h3 class="h4 brand-font mb-3 fw-bold text-uppercase">Открытые вилки</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">Зарплата известна до собеседования. Уважаем ваше время и не играем в угадайку на финальном оффере.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 magazine-col bg-white border-0">
                <h2 class="display-5 brand-font mb-4 fw-bold">03</h2>
                <h3 class="h4 brand-font mb-3 fw-bold text-uppercase">Строгий отбор компаний</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">В нашем списке нет галер. Только продуктовые команды, современные стеки и адекватные процессы.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="jobs-section py-5 px-5">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-end mb-5">
            <h2 class="display-4 brand-font mb-0 fw-bold text-uppercase">Свежие инжекты</h2>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-dark rounded-0 border-dark border-2 px-4 py-2 fw-bold text-uppercase">
                Смотреть все
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-4">
                <div class="card card-brutal p-4 h-100 bg-white border-dark border-2 rounded-0">
                    <h4 class="brand-font fw-bold mb-3 text-uppercase">Senior Frontend Engineer</h4>
                    <div class="text-accent fw-bold fs-5 mb-2">350K - 450K ₽</div>
                    <div class="small fw-bold mb-4">
                        FinTech Core &bull; <span class="text-secondary fw-normal">Москва / Remote</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr class="border-dark opacity-100 mt-auto mb-3">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="badge border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0 px-2 py-1">REACT</span>
                        <span class="badge border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0 px-2 py-1">TYPESCRIPT</span>
                        <span class="badge border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0 px-2 py-1">FSD</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-4">
                <div class="card card-brutal p-4 h-100 bg-white border-dark border-2 rounded-0">
                    <h4 class="brand-font fw-bold mb-3 text-uppercase">Go Backend Developer</h4>
                    <div class="text-accent fw-bold fs-5 mb-2">€4000 - €6000</div>
                    <div class="small fw-bold mb-4">
                        StreamData &bull; <span class="text-secondary fw-normal">Remote</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr class="border-dark opacity-100 mt-auto mb-3">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="badge border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0 px-2 py-1">GOLANG</span>
                        <span class="badge border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0 px-2 py-1">POSTGRESQL</span>
                        <span class="badge border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0 px-2 py-1">KAFKA</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-4">
                <div class="card card-brutal p-4 h-100 bg-white border-dark border-2 rounded-0">
                    <h4 class="brand-font fw-bold mb-3 text-uppercase">Lead DevOps / SRE</h4>
                    <div class="text-accent fw-bold fs-5 mb-2">ОТ 400 000 ₽</div>
                    <div class="small fw-bold mb-4">
                        CloudNexus &bull; <span class="text-secondary fw-normal">Санкт-Петербург / Office</span>
                    </div>
                    <hr class="border-dark opacity-100 mt-auto mb-3">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="badge border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0 px-2 py-1">TERRAFORM</span>
                        <span class="badge border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0 px-2 py-1">ANSIBLE</span>
                        <span class="badge border-dark text-dark bg-white rounded-0 px-2 py-1">AWS</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="border-top border-dark border-2 py-5 px-5 bg-white">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-6">
                <h4 class="brand-font fw-bold text-uppercase mb-2">NULLPTR JOB BOARD</h4>
                <p class="text-secondary mb-0 w-75">Строгий отбор. Никаких скрытых условий. Только инженерия и хардкор.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6 text-end d-flex gap-4 justify-content-end align-items-center">
                <a href="#" class="nav-link fw-bold text-decoration-none text-uppercase text-dark p-0">About</a>
                <a href="#" class="nav-link fw-bold text-decoration-none text-uppercase text-dark p-0">Telegram</a>
                <a href="#" class="nav-link fw-bold text-decoration-none text-uppercase text-dark p-0">Github</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
